      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "I'M FABULOUS (4) last seen when scorching around the 435m at Sale in 24.32 for a half a length victory. Expected to go close again if runs up to latest time. FAST KNOCKDOWN (6) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth at this track, but was among the placings at this track three back. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. OUTSIDES (1) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at The Meadows over 600m behind Caco Magic (35.02) in a R/A FIN. Was in the money prior to that. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to his credit. Should be about the money. MEPUNGA LILLY (3) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
